replies.body:
Let's see if I can find an easy solution; you said you worked through FAQs, so you may have already done this, but my first thought is that a firewall may be 'unhappy' with something new in recent updates. I'd suggest going through [**firewall troubleshooting**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues#wq3) as well to make sure nothing funky's going on there. Also, if you haven't, [**be sure that your Graphics drivers are updated **](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752684#wq1)as well.

I gotta say it's irritating when that happens to me too; happens for a lot of things lately when something updates and suddenly all the things are working differently.
{{sticker:sg-shisa}}
